##### MF3: REACTION CROSS SECTIONS                                2628 1451
                                                                  2628 1451
All the data present in the following MT-sections have been       2628 1451
calculated with TALYS, possibly normalized to experimental data.  2628 1451
If the maximal cross section in an excitation function over the   2628 1451
whole energy range does not exceed 1.e-9 b, the MT-number is not  2628 1451
included. Cross sections lower than 1.e-20 b are assumed to have  2628 1451
no physical meaning and are set to zero. All MT numbers extend up 2628 1451
to the highest incident energy.                                   2628 1451
The following reaction channels/MT numbers are generally included:2628 1451
                                                                  2628 1451
- MT1      : Total cross section                                  2628 1451
                                                                  2628 1451
Calculated with the optical model over the whole energy range,    2628 1451
or partly reproduced using experimental data.                     2628 1451
                                                                  2628 1451
- MT2      : Elastic scattering cross section                     2628 1451
                                                                  2628 1451
Obtained by subtracting the non-elastic cross section from the    2628 1451
total cross section.                                              2628 1451
                                                                  2628 1451
- MT3      : Non-elastic cross section                            2628 1451
                                                                  2628 1451
Calculated with the optical model over the whole energy range.    2628 1451
                                                                  2628 1451
- MT4      : Total inelastic cross section                        2628 1451
                                                                  2628 1451
Sum of MT=51-91.                                                  2628 1451
                                                                  2628 1451
- MT5      : (n,anything) cross section                           2628 1451
